Package: PHEstatmethods
Type: Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Title: Common Public Health Statistics and their Confidence Intervals 
Description: Functions to calculate the following statistics:
    1. proportions and their CIs using Wilson score method
    2. rates and their CIs using Byar's or exact Poisson method
    3. DSRs and their CIs using Dobson method
    4. SMRs and their CIs using Byar's or exact Poisson method 
